    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/228903f7b6b1b82bcf68f4904979a8cb.avif?t=1741395027\" width=616 height=616 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>本游戏可能包含不适合所有年龄段的内容，或者可能不适合在工作中观看。</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>该游戏目前是一款个人制作，基于文字对话剧情的视觉小说，正在用AI技术进行画面优化，都市模拟的玩法在2.0才会加入，且届时会更换为UE5引擎进行重制。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于我正在进行整体画面的优化升级，暂时请不要购买，预计在年底更新提升画面加入配音的全新版本，由于是个人独立游戏作品开发较慢，如感兴趣请务必考虑加入愿望单支持一下。（2024.8.23）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于11月12月接了外包出门驻点停滞了进度，配音工作和女3线没有能够及时制作完成，<span class=\"bb_strike\">准备在2025.3.4参加视觉小说节并上线画质优化版</span>（2025.2.15）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工作量有些大没能赶上，目前还需要测试并修缮bug以及提交审核的流程，非常抱歉，存在顾虑可以等待后续折扣（2025.3.3）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/e93424868d6ee904eaf978f32bb62b26.avif?t=1741395027\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras_big/e93424868d6ee904eaf978f32bb62b26.avif?t=1741395027 width=800 height=868 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/edd6f87be1578265538fd045f0b12806.avif?t=1741395027\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras_big/edd6f87be1578265538fd045f0b12806.avif?t=1741395027 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/aea76877b8df3ccbeec1582f853e2907.avif?t=1741395027\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras_big/aea76877b8df3ccbeec1582f853e2907.avif?t=1741395027 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/b47755e5493d547e2d99a14b8ea119d4.avif?t=1741395027\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras_big/b47755e5493d547e2d99a14b8ea119d4.avif?t=1741395027 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/b7873316023447e157de0711d19fce4b.avif?t=1741395027\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras_big/b7873316023447e157de0711d19fce4b.avif?t=1741395027 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/3b90d86199c5b0b337fbf8b7bc1d43cb.avif?t=1741395027\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras_big/3b90d86199c5b0b337fbf8b7bc1d43cb.avif?t=1741395027 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/48f43131e72405236c603959d36dc2ec.avif?t=1741395027\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras_big/48f43131e72405236c603959d36dc2ec.avif?t=1741395027 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/6ee9abb114ab9846a6aec3074579477a.avif?t=1741395027\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras_big/6ee9abb114ab9846a6aec3074579477a.avif?t=1741395027 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中人名与剧本均是杜撰，与现实中同名人士没有关系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏你将作为一名刚从大学校园毕业的普通毕业生，你会如何选择你人生的发展方向？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为社畜拼命工作，或是为她的梦想倾尽全力，还是干脆利用一切机会，成为商业巨子？或是一蹶不振，途穷反遭俗眼白，感受人性的善恶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等待你的是与女主角不期的相遇，或是她为你准备的陷阱？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >均可以由自己的做抉择…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/715fcfdb0c9067f64fb5c67b12234a0a.avif?t=1741395027\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个人独立游戏制作，题材特殊，体验不同的写实人生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >live2d动态立绘角色，1080p级别清晰度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >登场角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/f7a7bfe2954edda28d9d358fe1ed0eb7.avif?t=1741395027\" width=616 height=2174 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806070/extras/6098357b0f593e47ace5debff5abd093.avif?t=1741395027\" width=616 height=3268 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏故事中有一小部分故事设定是来自工作室成员个人亲身经历的过往，项目制作初衷是想与广大的galgame做一些差别，感觉上会偏向社会现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >预计5个女主角线，1个隐藏女主角线路，1.0当前将开放3个女主角的故事线，另外的3个女主线路会以免费DLC方式在后期更新。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >工作室简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RicoStudio是于2019年10月份，由一个游戏美术回乡创业而成立，当前游戏是第一款制作完成的作品，由于在程序方面不是强项第一个作品选择了视觉小说，条件成熟后会开始进行RPG等类型游戏的个人开发，希望能够多多支持！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2022.1.9</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更新页面讯息，今后将由我个人继续进行游戏信息的更新。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近期解决的一些问题：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.手游版本已成功打包，并且建立了一套手游版本的生产规范；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.内部本地化语言文字切换已经有了解决方案；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.女4线，女5线的流程和剧本，制作完成了一半，预计能够在年前完成，年后开始绘图制作；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4.由于资金有限，本地化语言将会使用机器翻译，请见谅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女4线的故事与女5线的故事有一些关联性，当制作完成将会一同更新为1.2版本</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外一些工作也在进行中：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1，\t手游版本会考虑上架谷歌与AppStore，基本免费，但内容会受限，将没有DLC的内容，不会制作你懂的内容，会加入广告SDK，不完整，只作为一点营收和推广的手段；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2，下一步我工作室的作品，会想办法加入类似《心跳回忆》与《明星志愿》类的模拟经营玩法，但估计不会太早能制作成功，当前的游戏还请大家能够支持；【模拟经营在毕业生模拟器2.0会上线】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3，动态CG也会考虑制作，但没人手，将会花费较多时间，希望能保持耐心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外再进行一些抱歉动作，由于之前的内容由多各人制作，导致画面上有一些明显不同的水平呈现，后面的游戏制作将会由我个人进行严格的控制，尽量要将画面水平进行同一个水平的呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多信息，请造访一下工作室页面</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推特                </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Facebook       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >instagram       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱发电            </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微博                </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >taptap            [/B]</p>",
